data.description: This beautiful simi custom 4 bed home with a office, boasts updated finishes, beautiful lighting fixtures, vaulted ceiling and an open concept. The gorgeous kitchen features an 11 foot quartz kitchen island, gas stove and plenty of cabinetry to store all your kitchen appliances. Offering a split bedroom floor plan, there is a wing of the home that could easily be dedicated to accommodating guests for a short stay. The primary bedroom suite measures in at 16x15ft not including the en-suite and walk in closet! A spectacular home located with easy access to the Nampa greenbelt and WIlson pond, this is sure to go fast!
